data.description:
A property of superabundant potential! Ideal for social events, company retreats, weddings, private parties, etc., etc. This beautiful, quiet area has a 3/2 country home with an updated 1/1 guest house overlooking a fully stocked artesian well pond on 2.07 acres in West Ft Pierce.  Plenty of room for toys & pets! Octagon shed/chicken coop with power & water.  A 20X20 aluminum carport/pole barn on concrete slab with power & 2 paddle fans.  A huge 30'X130' (65' covered & 65' enclosed) aluminum carport/workshop building on concrete slab with power, water & LED lighting. RV hookup with 30-amp service & septic.  Property is fenced with remote control gate to allow easy access without leaving your vehicle. Definitely a unique property full of possibilities! Call for your personal tour today More details:
Main house--Metal roof 2015, Well in front re-sleaved 2022, water softener new pump 2022, new reverse osmosis 2023
Guest house--Metal roof 2022, new AC 2022, air return in each room, 6" insulation in ceiling, impact windows, wood looking tile throughout, attic access in bedroom, built in closet shelves, rain shower, kitchen features newer stainless LG appliances, granite countertops, drop-in barn sink, custom pantry door, 
Pond--600 ft artesian well, water wheel, dock, ducks & geese, stocked with bass, brim, catfish & tilapia, water source
